name: A tribute to PapaBearded, Vol I
description:
I'll airdrop Papa two editions and also send half the profits of the remaining.

“In Africa, there are iridescent blues on the wings of birds that you do not see anywhere else in nature…” — Jodi Picoult

This little guy is called Lilac-breasted roller. I took this photo back in 2011 at Krueger’s National Park, in South Africa.
